### Required features
Include all of the following features from the idea:

#### 1) Automated trainee lifecycle tracking
Track trainees from onboarding to deployment readiness. Show status progression, stage completion, assessment attempts, score history, gaps between stages, and readiness indicators [1].

#### 2) Score aggregation and talent identification
Aggregate assessment scores automatically and identify top performers, average performers, and low performers. Highlight deserving talent based on performance trends, competency strength, and consistency [1].

#### 3) Role-based dashboards
Create real-time dashboards for each role [1]:
- **Trainer Dashboard:** batch-level progress, trainee details, performance summaries, alerts, module completion, and intervention recommendations.
- **LD / HR Dashboard:** organization-wide analytics, batch comparisons, trend analysis, cohort performance, and training effectiveness.
- **Business Stakeholder Dashboard:** deployment readiness, high-level batch outcomes, talent pool visibility, and strategic insights.
- **Admin Dashboard:** user management, system health, alert monitoring, tickets, access control, and operational oversight.

#### 4) Exportable reports
Allow exporting reports in **PDF and Excel** formats [1]. Include batch reports, trainee summaries, performance reports, risk reports, and readiness reports.

#### 5) AI/GenAI features
